Gamescom is one of the biggest gaming-events in the world, and once again it took place in Cologne, Germany, in August 2017. One of the games that was played at the most recent Gamescom is Blade & Soul - a fantasy martial-arts third person shooter video game first released in Korea back in 2012.

DOTA 2 ESL One is back this time from Hamburg. It is the eighth time and ESL's first ever event in the Barclaycard Arena of Hamburg. Only the best teams are ready to compete in the ESL One Hamburg, where the prestigious prize pool is $1,000,000 USD.

Welcome to Intel Extreme Masters Sydney. Across three action packed days from May 4th to 6th, a nation unites as the best fans join forces with the best teams to create one of the most memorable CS:GO tournaments. Join us at Qudos Bank Arena, in Sydney Olympic Park, for three days of fun, epicness and entertainment!
